U-Boot for NOVAsom S
--------------------

This file contains information for the port of U-Boot to the NOVAsom S.

NOVAsom S is a board that has three variants based on the following
SoCs: mx6 quad, mx6 dual lite and mx6 solo.

For more details about NOVAsom S, please refer to:
http://www.novasomindustries.org/

Building U-boot for NOVAsom S
-----------------------------

To build U-Boot for the NOVAsom S:

$ make novasoms_config
$ make

Flashing U-boot into the SD card
--------------------------------

- After the 'make' command completes, the generated 'SPL' binary must be
flashed into the SD card;
  $ ./flash

- Connect the serial cable to the host PC

- Power up the board and U-boot messages will appear in the serial console.
